{}

### ================= MODULE: Assessments =================
### [Module/Flow]: Training Execution
[Core Responsibility]: Records a score for a specific assessment.
[Target Audience]: Instructor, Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Assessments/record
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assessmentId": 1,
  "accountId": 1,
  "subjectResultId": 1,
  "score": 1,
  "remark": "string"
}

### [Module/Flow]: Training Execution
[Core Responsibility]: Signs off a subject result.
[Target Audience]: Instructor, Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Assessments/signoff
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjectResultId": 1,
  "role": "string",
  "comment": "string"
}

### [Module/Flow]: Training Execution
[Core Responsibility]: Retrieves assessment results for a specific student in a class.
[Target Audience]: Instructor, Admin, Student
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Assessments/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ================= MODULE: Attendance =================
### [Module/Flow]: Training Execution
[Core Responsibility]: Records attendance for a specific session.
[Target Audience]: Instructor, Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Attendance/record
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": 1,
  "classStudentId": 1,
  "status": "string",
  "remarks": "string"
}

### [Module/Flow]: Training Execution
[Core Responsibility]: Confirms that an attendance session has been finalized.
[Target Audience]: Instructor, Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Attendance/sessions/1/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### [Module/Flow]: Training Execution
[Core Responsibility]: Retrieves attendance records for a specific student in a class.
[Target Audience]: Instructor, Admin, Student
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Attendance/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

